snippet.title: Best VGM 2064 - Demon's Crest - Memorial of the Fallen Ones
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 240 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xnmuncx1F0Q
Best VGM 351 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qtrFSnyvEX0

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Demon's Crest (1994)
Memorial of the Fallen Ones
Toshihiko Horiyama
